	abstract = {Nowadays, the striking proliferation of Big Data and the new scientific tools provided by the emerging field of Data Science finally pave the road to realize a longstanding dream of scientists and policy makers: drawing a comprehensive picture of human social behavior. Big Data, indeed, hide a huge amount of predictive power, which can be exploited by governments and companies to unveiling and understanding the complexity underlying our society.
